column2: SELECT TOP #   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,   p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,   p.psfMag_u, p.psfMag_g,   p.psfMag_r, p.psfMag_i,   p.psfMag_z, p.modelMag_u,   p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r,   p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,   s.specobjid, s.class,   s.z AS redshift INTO   mydb.DR9_galaxies_with_modMag FROM   PhotoObj AS p JOIN   SpecObj AS s ON   s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE s.z BETWEEN # AND #   AND s.class = &&&  ORDER BY NEWID()
